{"lemma":"ظَعْنِ","slug":"ظَعْنِ","root":"ظ.ع.ن","root_slug":"ظ-ع-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ظ-ع-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"ظَعْن","root":"ظعن","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27551","n27554"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B8%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%92%D9%86%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to set out on a journey; to travel; to journey; to fare; to venture out or forth","tags":["intransitive","literary"],"examples":[{"text":"ظَعَنْتُ إِلَى دِمْيَاطَ. عَامَ هِياطٍ وَمِيَاطٍ. وَأَنَا يَوْمَئِذٍ مَرْمُوقُ ٱلرَّخَاءِ. مَوْمُوقُ ٱلْإِخَاءِ. أَسْحَبُ مَطَارِفَ ٱلثَّرَاءِ. وَأَجْتَلِي مَعَارِفَ ٱلسَّرَّاءِ.","english":"I fared off to Damietta, in a year of hurry-scurry, in arresting luxury, and prized fraternity, pulling along the tails of plenty, relishing visages of felicity."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of ظَعَنَ (ẓaʕana) (form I)","tags":["form-of","intransitive","literary","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Cognate to Aramaic טְעַן (ṭəʿan, “to carry”) and Hebrew צָעַן (ṣāʿán, “to wander”)."},"ipa":["/ðˤa.ʕa.na/","/ðˤaʕn/","/ðˤa.ʕan/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27551","headword_ar":"ظَعَنَ","root":"ZEn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaEonN","text_ar":"ظَعْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaEanN","text_ar":"ظَعَنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) or the latter is a simple subst., (Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZuEuwnN","text_ar":"ظُعُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maZoEanN","text_ar":"مَظْعَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", occurring in a verse of Zuheyr cited in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"blw","text_ar":"بلو"},{"kind":"text","text":", conj. 3],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He journeyed, went away, departed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Msb, K, * TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"removed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he journeyed to seek after herbage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to water;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he removed from water to water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from one country,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tract of land, to another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. [See also the part. n.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaAEinN","text_ar":"ظَاعِنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaEana bihi","text_ar":"ظَعَنَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n27554","headword_ar":"ظَعَنٌ","root":"ZEn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 1:       -A2-  and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZaAEinN","text_ar":"ظَاعِنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}